---
title: Seared Chicken & Confit Cherry Tomato Pasta Take your cooking skills to the next level!
description: Time to unleash your inner chef! Tonight’s pasta dinner is extra fancy - we’re going to confit the tomatoes to create a sweet and savoury sauce that allows this humble produce to shine. Garlic, herbs and chilli all add to the flavour, and with a slice of tender seared chicken on top, you won’t be able to resist this show-stopping meal.

